tools.description:
Retrieve all attributes of a user by user_id.

Args:
    user_id (str): The unique ID of the user to look up.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": UserInfo  # User attributes dictionary
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str  # Reason for failure, e.g., "User does not exist"
    }
